  "title": "Air-Fried Nutty Mediterranean Cashews Stir-fry",
  "description": "This nutty, tender mediterranean dish features flat rice noodles and is perfect for a cozy snack that's both halal-friendly and gluten-free.",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean",
