  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your air fryer to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, mix together cashews and flat rice noodles.",
    "Add olives, chopped parsley, and minced garlic to the mixture.",
    "Drizzle olive oil over the ingredients and stir well to coat.",
    "Transfer the mixture into your air fryer basket.",
    "Air fry for 8-10 minutes or until golden brown and crispy."
